snippet.title: DJSemtex
snippet.description: DJ Semtex moves crowds, works with the biggest artists, tears down shows and is an award-winning British DJ, broadcaster, author and producer with his finger firmly on the pulse. With a career spanning multiple decades, Semtex has played a vital role in bridging the gap between some of the hottest emerging talent on both sides of the Atlantic. Whether introducing listeners to the sounds of an early J. Cole, Kendrick Lamar or Kanye West via his historic Friday night hip hop show, securing world exclusive interviews with mavens such as Drake and DJ Khaled, or hosting in depth talks with Joe Budden, Dave, Stefflon Don and Giggs as host of Spotify’s Who We Be TALKS_ podcast, Semtex leads the way in providing platforms for the voices of the voiceless.
